  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sri Lanka: Development of a Labour Migration Strategy for the Caregiving and Hospitality Sectors</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project proposes to assist Sri Lanka in developing a labour migration strategy focused on the caregiving and hospitality sectors, for which Sri Lanka has local capacity and is well-known for abroad. A technical committee under the Ministry of Foreign Employment with key government officials, UN agencies and private sector stakeholders will be established to work on this task.</narrative>
  </description>
